Key.English: If enabled, each unique object on the map will need to be categorised
Key.Chinesesimp: 如果启用，地图上的每个唯一对象都需要分类

Key.English: Enter the path and filename of the map pbo relative to Arma 3 root directory.
Key.Chinesesimp: 输入映射pbo相对于Arma 3根目录的路径和文件名。

Key.English: Map bound value must cover the entire map and be rounded up to nearest 1000. By default uses worldSize/mapSize
Key.Chinesesimp: 地图绑定值必须覆盖整个地图,并四舍五入到最接近1000。默认使用worldSize/mapSize

Key.English: Only one Map Indexer module can be used
Key.Chinesesimp: 只能使用一个地图索引器模块

Key.English: If map indexer crashes, try changing the operating system selection here.
Key.Chinesesimp: 如果映射索引器崩溃，请尝试在这里更改操作系统选择。
